2. SUSTAINABILITY COORDINATOR
GreenBuild Construction Corp
Location: Makati City, Metro Manila
We are a leading construction firm specializing in BERDE-certified green buildings. Our portfolio includes commercial towers, mixed-use developments, and eco-friendly residential projects. We need a passionate individual to help us stay at the forefront of sustainable construction practices.
WHAT YOU'LL DO:

Coordinate BERDE certification process for all company projects
Monitor energy and water consumption data across active construction sites
Develop sustainability training modules for project managers and site workers
Liaise with Philippine Green Building Council and other industry partners

REQUIREMENTS:

Bachelor's degree in Environmental Science, Engineering, or related field
2+ years in sustainability, green building, or environmental compliance
Knowledge of BERDE rating system highly valued
Excellent communication and documentation skills

Contract position (1-year renewable)
Closing date: November 30, 2025